author: Nintendo of America
description:
Ranching is coming to Cult of the Lamb in the Woolhaven expansion in early 2026 on Nintendo Switch!  

Rebuild the flock and reawaken winter. Name your animals, care for them, harvest their goods, and train your followers to become ranch hands. 

 #NintendoSwitch #CultoftheLamb
